### Customer CRUD API Tests
### Make sure to first authenticate and get an auth token from the VerifyOtp endpoint

### 1. Get Customer Information (includes cars)
GET https://localhost:5001/customer/info
Authorization: Bearer eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6IlRYbCJ9..ym91xkcsXog3xHe5O8y2mGIekau9lOIU9mIx8RJxWlQ
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Update Customer Information
PUT https://localhost:5001/customer/info
Authorization: Bearer eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6IlRYbCJ9..JBKkiJWrsSaXyR0FQl3IxolMuDS4NSIRIp4sUHmP7Jg
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Vlad Crișan",
  "city": "New City",
  "address": "456 New St",
  "postalCode": "67890",
}

###

### 3. Add New Car
POST https://localhost:5001/customer/cars
Authorization: Bearer eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6IlRYbCJ9..JBKkiJWrsSaXyR0FQl3IxolMuDS4NSIRIp4sUHmP7Jg
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "licensePlate": "ABC123",
  "brand": "BMW",
  "model": "5"
}

###

### 4. Update Car Information
PUT https://localhost:5001/customer/cars/f54da7fe9e6c4edcbbd09bb7b9a47e6c
Authorization: Bearer eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6IlRYbCJ9..ym91xkcsXog3xHe5O8y2mGIekau9lOIU9mIx8RJxWlQ
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "licensePlate": "M1234"
}

###

### 5. Delete Car
DELETE https://localhost:5001/customer/cars/ef6679ce4f0042acb6e176960a75d44a
Authorization: Bearer eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6IlRYbCJ9..ym91xkcsXog3xHe5O8y2mGIekau9lOIU9mIx8RJxWlQ
Accept: application/json

###

### Example: Complete authentication flow first
### Step 1: Sign in to get OTP
POST https://localhost:5001/auth/customer/signin
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "vlad.crishan20@gmail.com"
}

###

### Step 2: Verify OTP to get auth token
POST https://localhost:5001/auth/verify-otp
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "vlad.crishan20@gmail.com",
  "code": "237873"
}

### Copy the authToken from the response above and use it in the Authorization header for the customer CRUD endpoints
